data.description: Spacious 5 Bedroom 3 Full bath home located in Countryview Addition Subdivision and has approximately 3,000+ sq feet of living space. Roof is approx. 2.5 years old! This home home has a lot to offer to a large family or anyone needing an unbelievably amount of space! You will enter into a spacious open floor plan. Kitchen has an island with additional storage & seating, beautiful hardwood floors, an area for a large table, plenty of counter space and cabinets and elegant French doors that walks out to a spacious deck that overlooks a huge fenced in backyard! The living room has beautiful cathedral ceilings and a gorgeous window letting in natural sunlight throughout! All of the 5 bedrooms are Immensely large with huge closets. The primary bedroom faces the backyard for additional privacy, has a large walk-in closet and the en-suite has a jetted tub, double sinks, cute storage cubie and a walk-in shower. Basement has new flooring throughout. Two spacious bedrooms are located in the basement along with another living room, another area that could be partitioned off (could be another bedroom, office, ect.), full bathroom and laundry room. Basement living room walkouts out onto a patio. Located in Countryview Addition, the subdivision swimming pool is at the entrance of the subdivision, not far from home! Come and get settled in just in time for summer fun at the pool, entertaining outdoors on the large deck overlooking the spacious fenced in backyard!
